import React from 'react'
import {
  FormControl,
  FormLabel,
  FormErrorMessage,
  FormHelperText,
  Input,
  Select
} from '@chakra-ui/react'

const ExpenseForm = () => {
  return(
    <FormControl>
      <FormLabel>Country</FormLabel>
      <Select placeholder='Select Entity'>
        <option>Alice</option>
        <option>Damaris</option>
        <option>Joana</option>
      </Select>
      <FormLabel>Vendor</FormLabel>
      <Input type='text' />
      <FormHelperText>Where did you create this expense.</FormHelperText>
      <FormLabel>Amount</FormLabel>
      <NumberInput max={50} min={10}>
        <NumberInputField />
        <NumberInputStepper>
          <NumberIncrementStepper />
          <NumberDecrementStepper />
        </NumberInputStepper>
      </NumberInput>
    </FormControl>
  )
}

export default ExpenseForm
